{"id:": "/div[1]", "tag": "div", "attributes": {"type": "article", "{http://www.w3.org/XML/1998/namespace}id": "MG-1685-05_086", "resp": "wordpro"}, "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/head[1]", "tag": "head", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/head[1]/text()[1]", "text": "[Madrigal sur la religion réformée]*"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]", "tag": "bibl", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/title[1]", "tag": "title", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/title[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Mercure galant"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/text()[1]", "text": ", mai 1685 [tome 5], p. 86-89"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[1]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Je ne sçaurois finir cet Article sans vous faire part d’un Madrigal qui enferme une Réponse aussi juste que spirituelle, faite par un Ministre de la Religion Prétenduë Reformée dans le Païs des Sevenes, Homme fort estimé parmy ceux de son Party, mais qui a fait voir une fidélité particuliere pour son Prince en toutes sortes d’occasions, quelque préoccupation qu’il ait pour la Religion qu’il professe. Le Madrigal explique le Fait."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]", "tag": "quote", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]", "tag": "lg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[1]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[1]/text()[1]", "text": " Dans une certaine Province"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[2]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[2]/text()[1]", "text": " Où nôtre incomparble Prince"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[3]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[3]/text()[1]", "text": "Souffre encor ceux qu’on dit Reformez Prétendus,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[4]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[4]/text()[1]", "text": "Où les Presches publics ne sont pas défendus,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[5]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[5]/text()[1]", "text": "En un Lieu qu’on a veu peu souvent dans l’Histoire,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[6]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[6]/text()[1]", "text": "Il arriva debat dedans le Consistoire."}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[7]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[7]/text()[1]", "text": "L’on reçoit dans ce Corps des Gens de tout état,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[8]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[8]/text()[1]", "text": "Le petit Artisan, tout comme l’Avocat,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[9]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[9]/text()[1]", "text": "Et mesme à cet honneur la force du sufrage"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[10]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[10]/text()[1]", "text": "Mieux que la pieté peut frayer le passage."}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[11]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[11]/text()[1]", "text": "Cependant un Tailleur ayant esté nommé,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[12]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[12]/text()[1]", "text": "Ce choix par quelques-uns ne fut pas confirmé."}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[13]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[13]/text()[1]", "text": " Sur ce Fait, au lieu de Sentence,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[14]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[14]/text()[1]", "text": "Le Ministre est prié de dire ce qu’il pense."}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/